=== Practical 6: Factorial ===


:- initialization(main).

factorial(0, 1).
factorial(N, F) :- N > 0, M is N-1, factorial(M, FM), F is N * FM.

main :-
    write('=== Practical Factorial ==='), nl, nl,
    factorial(0, R0), write('0! = '), write(R0), nl,
    factorial(5, R5), write('5! = '), write(R5), nl,
    factorial(7, R7), write('7! = '), write(R7), nl.


###Output


=== Practical Factorial ===

0! = 1
5! = 120
7! = 5040
